Compression: tar & gzip
Logging: Custom Log File (/var/log/devops-backup/backup.log)
1. Objective

The objective of this project was to design and implement a production-grade automated backup and disaster recovery solution for a Linux application. The project focused on automating backups using Bash scripting, scheduling execution with Cron, implementing centralized logging and error handling, configuring backup retention policies, performing disaster recovery testing through restoration, and securely storing backups in Amazon S3 for off-site disaster recovery.

